      <h2>France</h2>
      <p>France is a country that offers a rich diversity of landscapes, culture, history and cuisine. Whether you are looking for romance in Paris, art and architecture in Lyon, wine and gastronomy in Bordeaux, or sun and sea in Nice, you will find something to suit your taste and budget. France has a long and proud heritage that can be seen in its monuments, museums, castles and cathedrals. You can also explore the natural beauty of the country, from the Alps to the Pyrenees, from the Loire Valley to the Côte d'Azur. France is a destination that will enchant you with its charm and elegance.</p>
      
